        Construct a Computer.
        Parameters:
        computerURI - the computer URI.
        possibleFrequencies - the possible frequencies for cores.
        processingPower - the Mips for the different possible frequencies.
        defaultFrequency - the default frequency at which the cores run.
        maxFrequencyGap - the max frequency gap among cores of the same processor.
        numberOfProcessors - the number of processors in the computer.
        numberOfCores - the number of cores per processor (homogeneous).
        computerServicesInboundPortURI - the URI of the computer service inbound port.
        computerStaticStateDataInboundPortURI - the URI of the computer static data notification inbound port.
        computerDynamicStateDataInboundPortURI - the URI of the computer dynamic data notification inbound port.
        coreManagerInboundPortURI - the core management inbound port URI.

        java.lang.Exception - throws an exception if an error occured..
